SELECT [r].[Id], COALESCE([r].[MenuId], 0) AS [MenuId], COALESCE([r].[SubMenuId], 0) AS [SubMenuId], COALESCE([r].[RoleId], 0) AS [RoleId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [m0].[Name]
    FROM [Menu] AS [m0]
    WHERE [m0].[Id] = [r].[SubMenuId]) AS [SubMenuName], [m].[Name] AS [MenuName], [r0].[Name] AS [RoleName]
FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
LEFT JOIN [Menu] AS [m] ON [r].[MenuId] = [m].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Roles] AS [r0] ON [r].[RoleId] = [r0].[Id]

SELECT [r].[Id], COALESCE([r].[MenuId], 0) AS [MenuId], COALESCE([r].[SubMenuId], 0) AS [SubMenuId], COALESCE([r].[RoleId], 0) AS [RoleId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [m0].[Name]
    FROM [Menu] AS [m0]
    WHERE [m0].[Id] = [r].[SubMenuId]) AS [SubMenuName], [m].[Name] AS [MenuName], [r0].[Name] AS [RoleName]
FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
LEFT JOIN [Menu] AS [m] ON [r].[MenuId] = [m].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Roles] AS [r0] ON [r].[RoleId] = [r0].[Id]

SELECT [r].[Id], COALESCE([r].[MenuId], 0) AS [MenuId], COALESCE([r].[SubMenuId], 0) AS [SubMenuId], COALESCE([r].[RoleId], 0) AS [RoleId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [m0].[Name]

SELECT [r].[Id], COALESCE([r].[MenuId], 0) AS [MenuId], COALESCE([r].[SubMenuId], 0) AS [SubMenuId], COALESCE([r].[RoleId], 0) AS [RoleId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [m0].[Name]
    FROM [Menu] AS [m0]
    WHERE [m0].[Id] = [r].[SubMenuId]) AS [SubMenuName], [m].[Name] AS [MenuName], [r0].[Name] AS [RoleName]
FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
LEFT JOIN [Menu] AS [m] ON [r].[MenuId] = [m].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Roles] AS [r0] ON [r].[RoleId] = [r0].[Id]

SELECT [r].[Id], COALESCE([r].[MenuId], 0) AS [MenuId], COALESCE([r].[SubMenuId], 0) AS [SubMenuId], COALESCE([r].[RoleId], 0) AS [RoleId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [m0].[Name]
    FROM [Menu] AS [m0]
    WHERE [m0].[Id] = [r].[SubMenuId]) AS [SubMenuName], [m].[Name] AS [MenuName], [r0].[Name] AS [RoleName]
FROM [RoleMenuPermission] AS [r]
LEFT JOIN [Menu] AS [m] ON [r].[MenuId] = [m].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Roles] AS [r0] ON [r].[RoleId] = [r0].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [f].[Id], [f].[CommunityId], [f].[CreatedBy], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[FacilityDetails], [f].[FacilityLocation], [f].[FacilityName], [f].[FacilityTypeId], [f].[Rate], [f].[UpdatedBy], [f].[UpdatedDate], [f0].[Id] AS [Id0], [f0].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy0], [f0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [f0].[Name], [f0].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy0], [f0].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[Address], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId] AS [CommunityId0], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], [c].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate1]

) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CommunityId], [t].[CreatedBy], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[FacilityDetails], [t].[FacilityLocation], [t].[FacilityName], [t].[FacilityTypeId], [t].[Rate], [t].[UpdatedBy], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedBy0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t].[UpdatedBy0], [t].[UpdatedDate0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Address], [t].[CityName], [t].[CommunityId0], [t].[CommunityName], [t].[CommunityTypeId], [t].[CreatedBy1], [t].[CreatedDate1], [t].[FeesMonthly], [t].[GracePeriod], [t].[NoOfParkingLot], [t].[NoOfUnits], [t].[PICEmail], [t].[PICMobile], [t].[PICName], [t].[StateId], [t].[UpdatedBy1], [t].[UpdatedDate1], [f1].[Id], [f1].[CreatedBy], [f1].[CreatedDate], [f1].[FacilityId], [f1].[ImageGuid], [f1].[Name], [f1].[Preview], [f1].[UpdatedBy], [f1].[UpdatedDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [f].[Id], [f].[CommunityId], [f].[CreatedBy], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[FacilityDetails], [f].[FacilityLocation], [f].[FacilityName], [f].[FacilityTypeId], [f].[Rate], [f].[UpdatedBy], [f].[UpdatedDate], [f0].[Id] AS [Id0], [f0].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy0], [f0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [f0].[Name], [f0].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy0], [f0].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[Address], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId] AS [CommunityId0], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], [c].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate1]
    FROM [Facility] AS [f]
    INNER JOIN [FacilityType] AS [f0] ON [f].[FacilityTypeId] = [f0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Community] AS [c] ON [f].[CommunityId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [FacilityPhoto] AS [f1] ON [t].[Id] = [f1].[FacilityId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CommunityId], [t].[CreatedBy], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[FacilityDetails], [t].[FacilityLocation], [t].[FacilityName], [t].[FacilityTypeId], [t].[Rate], [t].[UpdatedBy], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedBy0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t].[UpdatedBy0], [t].[UpdatedDate0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Address], [t].[CityName], [t].[CommunityId0], [t].[CommunityName], [t].[CommunityTypeId], [t].[CreatedBy1], [t].[CreatedDate1], [t].[FeesMonthly], [t].[GracePeriod], [t].[NoOfParkingLot], [t].[NoOfUnits], [t].[PICEmail], [t].[PICMobile], [t].[PICName], [t].[StateId], [t].[UpdatedBy1], [t].[UpdatedDate1], [f1].[Id], [f1].[CreatedBy], [f1].[CreatedDate], [f1].[FacilityId], [f1].[ImageGuid], [f1].[Name], [f1].[Preview], [f1].[UpdatedBy], [f1].[UpdatedDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [f].[Id], [f].[CommunityId], [f].[CreatedBy], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[FacilityDetails], [f].[FacilityLocation], [f].[FacilityName], [f].[FacilityTypeId], [f].[Rate], [f].[UpdatedBy], [f].[UpdatedDate], [f0].[Id] AS [Id0], [f0].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy0], [f0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [f0].[Name], [f0].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy0], [f0].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[Address], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId] AS [CommunityId0], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy1], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy1], [c].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate1]
    FROM [Facility] AS [f]
    INNER JOIN [FacilityType] AS [f0] ON [f].[FacilityTypeId] = [f0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Community] AS [c] ON [f].[CommunityId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [FacilityPhoto] AS [f1] ON [t].[Id] = [f1].[FacilityId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]
